This repository vendors no third-party source. CI clones ngspice at the pinned ref
(upstream.yaml) and BUILDS it headless (--without-x, --enable-osdi). The built
artifact is ngspice — modified-BSD core with some GPL XSPICE code models — and each
bundle ships ngspice's own license as LICENSE.ngspice.

ngspice: https://ngspice.sourceforge.io/
